h1. doAuthPlugin
Basic authorization plugin

h2. Current features
* only one model: User. Easily applies to project. Simplifies project models logic.
* user validation (as in sfGuard)
* remember filter (uses hashes stored in cookies), not uses additional tables.

h2. Plans (differences from sfGuard)
* push all needed user functionality into User model
* add support for emails
* send validation message by email
* send email when user forgot password
* registration form

* permission groups
* permission templates
* group profiles
* mail notifications integration (user and group)
* access logging
* current user sessions statistics with interrupt functionality
* system user notifications 

